MQA.JSONDeserializer

Deserializer for JSON feed data

This class is created and passed in as a parameter when using a MQA.RemoteCollection with JSON feeds.

Parameters

dataProcessor(string) Callback function to handle and process the returned data.  The callback must take a JSON data object as a parameter and return an array of shapes (MQA.Poi or MQA.ShapeOverlay).
